---
/* Optional: if you want to pass service data dynamically later,
   you can convert the card list into a JS array. */
---
    <!-- Pillars Section -->
 <section id="pillars" class="pillars section light-background">

  <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>Our Pillars</h2>
    <p>The Space Integrity Initiative advances ethical communication through shared standards, open resources, and collaborative action.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row gy-4">

      <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="service-item position-relative">
          <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-check icon"></i></div>
          <h4><a href="#" class="stretched-link">Ethical Communication Pledge</a></h4>
          <p>A commitment to accuracy, transparency, fairness, and evidence-based communication across the global space sector.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="service-item position-relative">
          <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-people icon"></i></div>
          <h4><a href="#" class="stretched-link">Community & Collaboration</a></h4>
          <p>A global network of communicators, marketers, academics, and organisations advancing responsible practices together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="service-item position-relative">
          <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-journal-richtext icon"></i></div>
          <h4><a href="#" class="stretched-link">Standards & Best Practices</a></h4>
          <p>Evidence-based guidelines and case studies to support ethical narratives, sustainability claims, and responsible space reporting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="service-item position-relative">
          <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-globe2 icon"></i></div>
          <h4><a href="#" class="stretched-link">Advocacy for Peaceful Space</a></h4>
          <p>Championing global norms, rejecting destructive ASAT activities, and promoting space as a domain for shared progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section><!-- /Pillars Section -->